product.title: Japanese Aesthetic Sakura Blossom City Break iPhone Case
product.body_html:
Grab one of these dreamy Japanese-themed Cherry Blossom iPhone Cases to give your phone a dreamy Sakura look and protection! With its aesthetically pleasing design, no one will mistake your phone for anyone else's. Made with a clear case, you can give your phone a personal touch with a photo of your favorite memories behind it! Add a custom, quirky touch to your phone, and be the envy of your friends!


Description:

  • High-quality TPU + IPC Cover
  • Compatible Brand: Apple iPhones
  • Function: Anti-knock. Dirt-resistant
  • Five designs available (Sold individually)
  • Clear casing

A durable flexible case that grips around the edges of your phone.

Make sure you select the correct iPhone when ordering. The phone is not sold with the phone case.
